+/**
+ * enum virtchnl2_action_types - Available actions for sideband flow steering
+ * @VIRTCHNL2_ACTION_DROP: Drop the packet
+ * @VIRTCHNL2_ACTION_PASSTHRU: Forward the packet to the next classifier/stage
